<h6 >Key Take aways </h6>
 </div> 
 
-  <font size="6">This is one of the rarely documented experience I ever recorded</font>
-  <font size="6"> But in fact I receive hundreds of  similar calls </font>
- <font size="6"> Customer calling about features we did not advertise </font>
-  <font size="6">But may have  heard about them from other buyers  </font>
-  <font size="6"> Other buyers feedback can be true but contextual </font>
-  <font size="6"> This shows a pattern of shopping on amazon </font>
-  <font size="6"> buyers rely more on social proof to make  buying decision </font>
- <font size="6"> than information provided by the sellers themselves </font>

