- <font size="6"> Buying decision may be based on reviews, feedback & testimonials than real information provided buy the sellers  </font>
- <font size="6"> This resulting into product social proof artificial creation as  its influence both buyers decision and ranking in various platform such as google, amazon etc ...  </font>

